spells.description: Use: Gain 4 stacks of Platinum Plating for 30 sec, increasing your Armor by 9,828. Receiving more than 10% of your health from a Physical damage effect will remove one stack of Platinum Plating. (2 Min Cooldown)

Equip: Your abilities have a chance to call the Darkness to you, increasing your Agility by 1,954, up to 9,774.

Upon reaching full power, the Darkness is unleashed, inflicting 1.7 million Shadow damage split between nearby enemies over 15 sec before fading back into the remnant.
Equip: You champion the causes of your guild.  All guild reputation gains are increased by 100%.
